headline.main: Wobbly Skylab Astronauts End 84-Day Orbital Flight; Wobbly Skylab Astronauts End 84-Day Orbit Flight

results.snippet: HOUSTON, Feb. 8--Wobbly-legged but cheerful, the Skylab 3 astronauts returned this morning from 84 days in orbit around the earth, man's longest space flight.

headline.main: OIL RESERVE SEARCH URGED BY EXPERTS
